= Build the latest stable version =
Download the source tarball from the [http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=202302 STK Download area]

 tar -xjvf supertuxkart-0.6.1a.tar.bz2
 cd supertuxkart-0.6
 ./configure && make
 sudo make install
and if it's OK, you can run STK:
 supertuxkart

= Build the latest unstable version (from SVN) =
Check out the sources using:
 svn co https://supertuxkart.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/supertuxkart/main/trunk
 cd supertuxkart
 ./autogen.sh && ./configure && make
 sudo make install
and if it's OK, you can run STK:
 supertuxkart

